title: Star Trek : 25th Anniversary
description:
Ladies and Gentlemen I Present to you Star Trek : 25th anniversary the collectors extended version 1992

THIS IS the extended Version with full original cast voice acting. Tested on Windows XP

GAME DESCRIPTION:
The game is divided into several seperate episodes, each of which features a space combat and away mission element. During the game, you will discover new races, meet up with an old friend, rescue another Federation Starship, fight in epic battles, and more! As well, there are many different possible ways to complete each mission, some better than others, which gives this game great replayability. At the end of each episode you&#039;ll be debriefed and graded on your mission by a Starfleet Admiral.
